    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streetball Fury is a fast paced mix of street basketball and brawling pixel art game, with unique characters, maps and cool tunes. Punch, kick or use your super attacks to get hold of the ball and score more points than your opponents by throwing, dunking or unleashing super FURY shots!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283400/extras/46c6e36340ad1ad921cd6b79ad47d6f5.poster.avif?t=1728997844\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283400/extras/46c6e36340ad1ad921cd6b79ad47d6f5.webm?t=1728997844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Morty and Nerd in solo or co-op campaign mode featuring a mysterious tournament to find the best streetball player. Play against your friends and foes in local  matches with up to 4 players.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fast-paced beat’em’up-basketball hybrid gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Various hand crafted characters and maps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Battle against AI or other people in local matches </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Short but challenging solo  campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Funky tunes </p></li></ul>",
